0whether%20asylum%20seekers%20were%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20officers%20were%20injured%20there%2C%20but%20local%20police%20said%20none%20of%20the%20hotel%20staff%20or%20its%20clients%20had%20been%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20northeastern%20English%20city%20of%20Middlesbrough%2C%20hundreds%20of%20protesters%20squared%20up%20to%20riot%20police%20carrying%20shields.%20Some%20threw%20bricks%2C%20cans%20and%20pots%20at%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20there%20seized%20a%20camera%20from%20an%20AFP%20crew%20and%20broke%20it.%20The%20journalists%20were%20not%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20disturbances%20came%20after%20police%20said%20more%20than%20150%20people%20had%20been%20arrested%20since%20Saturday%20following%20skirmishes%20at%20far-right%20rallies%20in%20Liverpool%2C%20Manchester%2C%20Bristol%2C%20Blackpool%20and%20Hull%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Belfast%20in%20Northern%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERioters%20threw%20bricks%2C%20bottles%20and%20flares%20at%20police%20--%20injuring%20several%20officers%20--%20and%20looted%20and%20burnt%20shops%2C%20while%20demonstrators%20shouted%20anti-Islamic%20slurs%20as%20they%20clashed%20with%20counter-protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20is%20the%20worst%20England%20has%20seen%20since%20summer%202011%2C%20when%20widespread%20rioting%20followed%20the%20police%20killing%20of%20a%20mixed-race%20man%20in%20north%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChristian%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Jewish%20religious%20leaders%20in%20Liverpool%20issued%20a%20joint%20appeal%20for%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20now%20seeing%20it%20(trouble)%20flooding%20across%20major%20cities%20and%20towns%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tiffany%20Lynch%20of%20the%20Police%20Federation%20of%20England%20and%20Wales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20Sunday%2C%20Staffordshire%20police%20said%20another%20hotel%20known%20to%20have%20sheltered%20asylum%20seekers%20was%20targeted%20near%20Birmingham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%2