20game%2C%20everything%20hurts.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20those%2010%20overs%20(when%20India%20lost%20six%20wickets%20for%2050%20runs).%20You%20have%20to%20play%20consistent%20cricket%20and%20we%20failed%20to%20do%20that.%20Little%20disappointed%20but%20these%20things%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%20%26quot%3BWe%20weren't%20good%20enough.%20Don't%20want%20to%20look%20too%20much%20into%20how%20we%20played.%20But%20there'll%20be%20talks%20about%20our%20batting%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20India%20batters%20need%20to%20adapt%20quickly%20to%20the%20pitches%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20got%20to%20adapt%20to%20what's%20in%20front%20of%20you.%20With%20left-right%20(combination%20of%20batsmen)%2C%20we%20felt%20it'll%20be%20easier%20to%20rotate%20strike.%20But%20credit%20to%20Jeffrey%2C%20he%20got%20six%20wickets.%26quot%3B%20The%2037-year-old%20said%20there%20will%20not%20be%20any%20change%20in%20his%20approach%20despite%20the%20setback%20in%20this%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I%20got%2065%20is%20because%20of%20the%20way%20I%20batted.%20When%20I%20am%20batting%20like%20that%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20risks%20taken.%20If%20you%20don't%20cross%20the%20line%2C%20you%20always%20feel%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20on%20my%20intent.%20We%20understand%20nature%20of%20this%20surface%2C%20it%20gets%20really%20tough%20in%20the%20middle%20overs.%20You%20have%20to%20try%20to%20get%20as%20many%20as%20possible%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESri%20Lankan%20skipper%20Charith%20Asalanka%20said%20their%20total%20of%20240%20was%20enough%20under%20the%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20happy%20with%20the%20score%20--%20240%20was%20good%20enough.%20As%20a%20captain%2C%20I%20like%20this%20kind%20of%20problems%20(plenty