%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%2C%20Hezbollah%20shares%20Tehran's%20core%20ideology%20and%20recruits%20primarily%20from%20Lebanon's%20Shiite%20Muslim%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20Hezbollah%20will%20escalate%20its%20attacks%20deeper%20into%20Israeli%20territory%2C%20potentially%20targeting%20more%20than%20just%20military%20installations.%20The%20rapid%20escalation%20of%20tensions%20follows%20Israel's%20recent%20assassination%20of%20a%20senior%20Hezbollah%20military%20commander%2C%20Fuad%20Shukr.%20On%20July%2030%2C%20Israel%20struck%20a%20densely%20populated%20residential%20area%20in%20south%20Beirut%2C%20killing%20Shukr%20and%20five%20civilians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20assassination%20of%20Hamas%20political%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20in%20Tehran%2C%20a%20move%20attributed%20to%20Israel%2C%20although%20it%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%20by%20Israeli%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20have%20heightened%20dramatically%2C%20as%20months%20of%20cross-border%20skirmishes%20risk%20devolving%20into%20a%20full-scale%20conflict%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel.%20The%20two%20adversaries%20last%20engaged%20in%20a%20devastating%20war%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202006%2C%20which%20saw%20Israel%20bombing%20Lebanon's%20only%20passenger%20airport%20in%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20the%20current%20situation%20has%20led%20various%20embassies%2C%20including%20India's%2C%20to%20urge%20their%20citizens%20to%20leave%20Lebanon%20while%20commercial%20flights%20remain%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20maintained%20near-daily%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20with%20Israeli%20forces%2C%20targeting%20military%20positions%20since%20its%20Palestinian%20ally%20Hamas%20initiated%20an%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20triggering%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20developments%2C%20Antony%20Blin