%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20is%20living%20out%20of%20a%20van%20while%20renovating%20the%20watermill.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20watched%20that%20very%20carefully.%20And%20in%20September%20of%202022%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-dollar-strong-europe-england-exchange-rates-american-travel-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20dollar%20was%20worth%20more%20than%20the%20Euro%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20so%20we%20were%20able%20to%20transfer%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20at%20that%20time%20to%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20Monchique%20mountains%2C%20about%2030%20minutes%20from%20the%20southern%20coast.%20The%20nearest%20village%20is%20about%2015%20minutes%20away%2C%20while%20the%20closest%20international%20airport%20is%20about%20an%20hour's%20drive%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%207%2C000%20people%2C%20so%20it's%20kind%20of%20an%20agricultural%20village%20in%20the%20mountains%20with%20many%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20said.%20From%20my%20understanding%2C%20the%20town%20was%20thriving%20in%20the%20'70s%20and%20the%20'80s%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20younger%20people%20have%20moved%20away%20to%20the%20cities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c53c7ef-84c0-4df1-9cb8-e79bf9bb3a21%5C%22%3ELiving%20on-site%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20slowly%20chipping%20away%20at%20renovating%20the%20property%20while%20living%20out%20of%20a%20van%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222544%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20with%20construction%20tools.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a0a58ffb2b6bedb059e7aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221699%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey're%20in%20the%20second%20year%20of%20their%20renovation%20project.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20starting%20work%20on%20the%20land%20or%20the%20watermill%2C%20we%20found%20a%20level%20spot.%20We%20installed%20our%20Starlink%20satellite%20pole.%20We%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20pump%20water%20from%20the%20stream%20into%20the%20tank%20that%20fills%20our%20camper%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittany%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-school-student-diy-van-tiny-home-gen-z-california-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelying%20on%20solar%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20camper%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20connect%20the%20watermill%20property%20to%20the%20grid%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20do%20a%20hybrid%20system%20because%2C%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20we%20just%20want%20that%20assurance.%20There%20can%20be%20weeks%20of%20gray%20skies%20that%20won't%20charge%20our%20solar%20panels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20watermill%20is%20on%20a%20commercial%20licensed%20property%2C%20the%20couple%20must%20follow%20certain%20rules%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20habitation%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20the%20watermill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669f58412d66759f66fd2cb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20watermill.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20is%20that%20we%20can't%20change%20the%20existing%20footprint%20of%20what%20was%20already%20approved%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20can't%20make%20the%20house%20larger.%20All%20we%20can%20do%20is%20go%20up%20and%20finish%20everything%20and%20then%20put%20in%20the%20electrical%20and%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20major%20part%20of%20the%20work%20was%20fixing%20the%20leaking%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20first%20came%20here%2C%20it%20was%20just%20gushing%20down%20whenever%20it%20rained%2C%20and%20we%20were%20putting%20buckets%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20couple%20is%20working%20on%20the%20project%20full-time%2C%20they%20also%20have%20a%20team%20of%20contractors%20helping%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Construction%20materials%20strewn%20all%20over%20the%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a9e22c1a227600e632fe80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20hired%20contractors%20to%20help%20them%20with%20the%20project.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-families-travel-abroad-kids-school-boundless-life-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20expat%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittany%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20every%20Friday%2C%20this%20community%20gets%20together.%20By%20gathering%20with%20them%20and%20asking%20questions%20or%20saying%20that%20we're%20looking%20for%20roofers%2C%20we%20found%20a%20wonderful%20team%20of%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20as%20much%20as%20the%20couple%20is%20excited%20to%20take%20on%20some%20renovation%20projects%2C%20certain%20tasks%20require%20technical%20skills%20that%20they%20lack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20built%20the%20roof%2C%20and%20they're%20currently%20helping%20us%20finish%20the%20parts%20that%20we%20can't%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20watermill's%20location%20in%20a%20relatively%20quiet%20area%2C%20the%20couple%20says%20getting%20the%20construction%20materials%20hasn't%20been%20too%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20standing%20amid%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20front%20of%20their%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a0a5902d66759f66fd9ebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20don't%20know%20exactly%20when%20the%20watermill%20was%20built%2C%20but%20they%20estimate%20it%20to%20be%20several%20hundred%20years%20old.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20couple%20being%20able%20to%20speak%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20Portuguese%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20language%20classes%20they've%20been%20taking%20twice%20a%20week%20for%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20it%20a%20sign%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20local%20people%20and%20culture%2C%20it%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20form%20friendships%20with%20the%20people%20they%20work%20with%2C%20Brittany%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20foreigner%20or%20something%2C%20it%20just%20really%20allows%20us%20to%20connect%20better%20with%20who%20we%20live%20around%20and%20who%20we%20hire%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9a86622-944c-48bb-94f4-d53e0676f3b5%5C%22%3ENavigating%20the%20challenges%20of%20designing%20a%20large%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20biggest%20challenge%20so%20far%20was%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20work%20with%20a%20larger%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20van%2C%20because%20it%20was%2080%20square%20feet%20and%20small%2C%20was%20very%20manageable%20for%20Brittany%20and%20me%20to%20do%20ourselves.%20This%20watermill%20project%2C%20we%20have%20to%20have%20other%20people%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20different%20from%20anything%20they'd%20done%20before%2C%20especially%20since%20they%20now%20had%20to%20coordinate%20a%20larger%20team%2C%20from%20finding%20the%20right%20contractors%20to%20managing%20project%20timelines%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-decor-mistakes-interior-designer-hates-to-see-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesigning%20the%20interior%20layout%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20watermill%20is%20very%20different%20from%20that%20of%20a%20van.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20used%20to%20living%20in%20such%20a%20small%20space%20and%20having%20one%20thing%20perform%20multiple%20tasks%20that%20having%20so%20much%20more%20space%20to%20build%20inside%20of%20feels%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittany%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222544%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20with%20construction%20tools.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a0a58ffb2b6bedb059e7ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221699%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20has%20been%20documenting%20their%20renovation%20journey%20on%20YouTube.%3Cp%3EMr%20and%20Mrs%20Adventure%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Drew%20added%2C%20even%20the%20bathroom%20in%20the%20watermill%20is%20about%20the%20size%20of%20their%20van.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-home-renovation-old-abandoned-cottage-scotland-before-after-photos-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovating%20an%20abandoned%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20couple%20says%20that%20they%20were%20prepared%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20before%20they%20started%20the%20process%20of%20purchasing%20the%20watermill%2C%20Drew's%20parents'%20home%20in%20Fort%20Myers%2C%20Florida%2C%20was%20devastated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbabcock-ranch-florida-solar-power-town-survived-hurricane-ian-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22