5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia's%20AI-powering%20microchips%20are%20finding%20their%20way%20to%20the%20Chinese%20military%20despite%20US%20efforts.%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%2C%20an%20American%20company%2C%20makes%20powerful%20chips%20that%20are%20fueling%20a%20global%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20limits%20the%20kind%20of%20chips%20Nvidia%20can%20sell%20in%20China%20to%20hinder%20the%20country's%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20smugglers%20are%20skirting%20the%20blockade%2C%20funneling%20chips%20to%20China's%20military%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20network%20of%20smugglers%20is%20helping%20the%20Chinese%20military%20obtain%20powerful%20microchips%20made%20by%20Nvidia%2C%20an%20American%20company%2C%20all%20under%20the%20nose%20of%20a%20US%20national%20security%20blockade%20meant%20to%20curb%20China's%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20is%20competing%20with%20China%20to%20dominate%20the%20AI%20industry.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20maintain%20its%20global%20dominance%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasml-shares-surge-us-government-china-crackdown-ai-chips-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20expand%20its%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20exports%20of%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20equipment%20to%20include%20Israel%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20also%20worries%20that%20advanced%20artificial%20intelligence%20could%20be%20used%20to%20modernize%20foreign%20militaries%2C%20which%20could%20threaten%20American%20security%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20chips%20are%20fueling%20the%20global%20AI%20boom%2C%20elevating%20the%20company%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20profitable%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20United%20States%20only%20allows%20Nvidia%20to%20sell%2