n.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20leader%20announced%20the%20use%20of%20F-16s%2C%20which%20Kyiv%20has%20long%20lobbied%20for%2C%20as%20he%20met%20military%20pilots%20at%20an%20air%20base%20flanked%20by%20two%20of%20the%20jets%20with%20two%20more%20flying%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BF-16s%20are%20in%20Ukraine.%20We%20did%20it.%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20our%20guys%20who%20are%20mastering%20these%20jets%20and%20have%20already%20started%20using%20them%20for%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20said%20at%20a%20location%20that%20authorities%20asked%20Reuters%20not%20to%20disclose%20for%20security%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20now%20in%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20development%20for%20the%20Air%20Force%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20Ukraine.%20We%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20transition%20the%20Ukrainian%20Air%20Force%20to%20a%20new%20aviation%20standard%20%E2%80%93%20Western%20combat%20aviation.%20From%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20war%2C%20we%20have%20been%20talking%20with%20our%20partners%20about%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz21yTU0Hjo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fz21yTU0Hjo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20%2F%20%D0%92%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%80%20%D0%97%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%81%D1%8C%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9%20(%40ZelenskyyUa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZelenskyyUa%2Fstatus%2F1820097797556765019%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%20the%20jets%20is%20a%20milestone%20for%20Ukraine%20after%20many%20months%20of%20waiting%2C%20though%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20many%20are%20available%20and%20how%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20they%20will%20have%20in%20enhancing%20air%20defences%20and%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20targeting%20bases%20that%20may%20house%20them%20and%20vowed%20to%20shoot%20them%20down%20so%20they%20will%20not%20impact%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20by%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20the%20F-16s%20had%20been%20on%20Ukraine's%20wish%20list%20for%20a%20long%20time%20because%20of%20their%20destructive%20power%20and%20global%20availability.%20They%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%2020mm%20cannon%20and%20can%20carry%20bombs%2C%20rockets%20and%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20tarmac%20of%20an%20airfield%2C%20Zelenskiy%20said%20Ukraine%20still%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20pilots%20trained%20to%20use%20the%20F-16s%20or%20enough%20of%20the%20jets%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20positive%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20are%20expecting%20additional%20F-16s%20...%20many%20guys%20are%20now%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20important%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20Kyiv's%20allies%20found%20ways%20to%20expand%20training%20programmes%20and%20opportunities%20for%20both%20Ukrainian%20pilots%20and%20engineering%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'NEW%20AVIATION%20STANDARD'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20previously%20relied%20on%20an%20ageing%20fleet%20of%20Soviet-era%20warplanes%20that%20are%20outgunned%20by%20Russia's%20more%20advanced%20and%20far%20more%20numerous%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20used%20that%20edge%20to%20conduct%20regular%20long-range%20missile%20strikes%20on%20targets%20across%20Ukraine%20and%20also%20to%20pound%20Ukrainian%20front%20line%20positions%20with%20thousands%20of%20guided%20bombs%2C%20supporting%20its%20forces%20that%20are%20slowly%20advancing%20in%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20new%20stage%20of%20development%20of%20the%20air%20force%20of%20Ukraine's%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20lot%20for%20Ukrainian%20forces%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20new%20aviation%20