es%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20lifeline%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20Sambhal%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20farmers%20depending%20on%20its%20water%20for%20irrigating%20their%20lush%20green%20paddy%20and%20peppermint%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20river%20that%20passes%20through%2071%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20five%20development%20blocks%20disappeared%20from%20the%20district%20due%20to%20large-scale%20encroachment%20and%20neglect.%20In%202022%2C%20when%20the%20newly-appointed%20district%20magistrate%20IAS%20Manish%20Bansal%20visited%20the%20field%2C%20he%20found%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20water%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20that%20the%20river%20was%20practically%20non-existent.%20We%20could%20only%20see%20small%20%3Cem%3Epuliya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(culverts)%20that%20were%20once%20made%20over%20the%20river.%20At%20several%20points%2C%20farmers%20had%20started%20growing%20crops%20considering%20it%20to%20be%20vacant%20land.%20The%20streak%20of%20the%20river%20was%20not%20completely%20connected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20some%20places%2C%20the%20area%20was%20covered%20in%20small%20puddles.%20The%20river%20was%20encroached%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20lost%20its%20path%20of%20natural%20flow%20downstream.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20nearby%20areas%20would%20remain%20waterlogged%20during%20monsoon.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20acted%20as%20a%20natural%20drainage%20system%20for%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20had%20drastically%20reduced%20in%20the%20area%20as%20farmers%20became%20dependent%20on%20borewells%2C%20which%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20water%20problem%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20hand%20pumps%2C%20as%20deep%20as%2050%20feet%2C%20started%20becoming%20non-functional%20because%20of%20the%20receding%20water%20table%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5