ng%5C%22%3EPaving%20a%20path%20for%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20Rachna%20almost%208-10%20hours%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20The%20price%20of%20each%20framed%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20ranges%20from%20Rs%201%2C000-3%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20work%20and%20its%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20part%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20sale%20is%20spent%20on%20raw%20material%20like%20wheat%20stalks%2C%20paying%20shop%20rent%20and%20electricity%20bills%2C%20Rachna%20is%20using%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20money%20to%20fund%20her%20dream%20to%20continue%20her%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20it%20was%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20success%20story%20that%20inspired%20most%20of%20these%20students%20to%20join%20her%20classes.%20When%20Pooja%20(17)%20heard%20about%20how%20Rachna%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20her%20life%20around%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20her%20painting%20and%20entrepreneurial%20skills%2C%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20do%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202016px)%20100vw%2C%202016px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0740_11zon-1722256630.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachna%20teaching%20her%20students%20at%20her%20shop%20and%20training%20centre.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0740_11zon-1722256630.jpg%202016w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0740_11zon-1722256630-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0740_11zon-1722256630-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.