utiful%20part%20of%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20CA%20Final%20attempt%20in%20May%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288421%2Fca-ishu-agrawal-shares-tips-on-how-he-cleared-upsc-cse-while-working%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esiblings%20started%20intense%20preparations%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20December%2C%20when%20their%20study%20leave%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20motivated%20each%20other%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20study%20plan%20was%20target-based%2C%20not%20time-based.%20They%20would%20decide%20what%20they%20had%20to%20complete%20each%20day.%20They%20first%20completed%20all%20pending%20lectures%20when%20their%20study%20leave%20started.%20The%20first%20subject%20they%20picked%20up%20in%20December%20was%20taxation.%20Their%20plan%20was%20divided%20into%2015-day%20chunks%2C%20each%20covering%20one%20practical%20and%20one%20theory%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-4